text: Nanfadima Magassouba is an activist of women's rights and a politician from Guinea. She was the head of the National Coalition of Guinea for the Rights and Citizenship of Women (CONAG-DCF), and a member of Guinea's National Assembly since 2013. == References == Category:Guinean politicians Category:Living people Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Women's rights activists
title: Nanfadima Magassouba
